            <h2>Methodology</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted);">
                Data for this S&P 500 earnings growth study was compiled using recent financial market data from all S&P 500 constituents.
                Companies are strictly ranked by their actual Year-over-Year (YoY) Earnings Growth (EPS Growth). We also include historical YoY Revenue Growth,
                Forward Price-to-Earnings (P/E), and Price/Earnings-to-Growth (PEG) ratios to provide a comprehensive valuation profile.
                Missing or unavailable data points are explicitly marked as "N/A". Data is restricted to the top 50 fastest growers with meaningful scale.
            </p>
